          <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6J-wB4FODQI?si=KkZ9RHdS7QFTAM8R" title="IoT e automação no agronegócio" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
